identifies biologically meaningful accumulations in metabolomic data

msea.Rd

This function performs Metabolite Set Enrichment Analysis (MSEA) with KEGG COMPOUND IDs.

msea(metabolite.set, mets.queryset, assessment = "E", midp = FALSE)

Arguments

metabolite.set

a list of metabolite sets
mets.queryset

a list of metabolites for which enrichment test is to be done
assessment

a kind of alternative test (E, enrichment; D, depletion; and ED, enrichment or depletion)
midp

logical. TRUE gives mid p-values

Value

msea object

Examples

data(mset_SMPDB_format_KEGG)
data(kusano)

res <- msea(mset_SMPDB_format_KEGG, kusano)
